TableContextTimeStampAfterTable: {15064=Order deadline - Friday, July 24th at 5pm, 16194=On Saturday, June 13th, members of EUPA joined together on the University of Alberta campus to participate in a rolling Ultimate game that spanned the country (and jumped to Dubai, Cambodia and Ireland!) in memory of a great Ultimate citizen Art Hawkins. Players took the field following a donation-only BBQ made possible by Cencomp Systems Solutions Inc and our own Curtis Barranoik (Drafted & Party Wolf)., 17627=To help make the most of summer with some fun pick-up Wednesday nights at Kaskitayo, we are looking for a few players to act as Pick-up Coordinators! We are currently looking to start pick-up the second week in June and continue to run games throughout the summer (interest permitting).
